enumerations.name: ListEnum
enumerations.note: This meta-class represents the notation of the various types of lists. Aggregated by List.type

literals.name: number
literals.description:
This indicates that the list is an numerated list.
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=0

literals.name: unnumber
literals.description:
This indicates that it is an enumeration (bulleted list)
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=1

enumerations.name: ItemLabelPosEnum
enumerations.note: This enumerator specifies, how the label of a labeled list shall be rendered. Aggregated by IndentSample.itemLabelPos

literals.name: newline
literals.description:
The label is renders in a new line.
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=0

literals.name: newlineIfNecessary
literals.description:
The label is rendered in a new line if it is longer than the indentation.
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=1

literals.name: noNewline
literals.description:
The label is rendered in one line with the item even if it is longer than the indentation.
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=2
